name: Personalized Photo Shoot Inspiration Board
description:
Do you have a photo shoot coming up, but find yourself stuck on what to wear? Wondering how to make the pictures pop and still have everyone look put together? I would love to help! E-mail general info about your shoot (people, place, time of year, special occasion) to: erin@bringingupburns.com
and I will customize an inspiration board for your shoot.

Your board will be sent in an email and includes:
*10-15 photos and credits for the images
*detailed ideas for clothing, accessories, and props and/or poses
*In addition, your board will be featured on the Bringing Up Burns blog for other readers to enjoy!
*Initial board is for 4 people. Each additional person will be $5.

Turn around time is typically 2 weeks per board from the receipt of payment.  Please contact me if you need it quicker!
